{"tid":2099004,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"✤✤✤✤✤✤【一人一post】7/11、7/12 初選記得要投票✤✤✤✤✤✤","createTime":"2020-07-08T02:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T14:46:23.000Z","uid":810,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"404b031ca912080097371ac7bcbb7edc91fe0764","tid":2099004,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:21:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要帶 (任一樣)<br />\n1. 住址證明<br />\n2. 官方選舉選民通知書<br />\n3. 選民登記網站截圖（呢度cap）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/index.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fmob%2Findex.jsp&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=619f8e9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/index.jsp</a><br />\n證明你係嗰區居民/選民<br />\n<br />\n用自己電話去票站scan qr code<br />\n喺app投票<br />\n票站有少量後備公家機<br />\n亦都有紙張票<br />\n<br />\n要填<br />\n1. 身分證後四位數字（唔包括號內數字）<br />\n2. 身分證簽發日期（年月日）<br />\n3. 出生日期（日期ONLY）<br />\n<br />\n票站：共251個票站（地點稍後公布）<br />\n主要<span style=\"color: red;\">議員辦事處</span>，有黃店，有街站<br />\n新西 6x個<br />\n新東 5x個<br />\n九東 44個<br />\n九西 約40個<br />\n港島 45個<br />\n三個票站專for衛生服務界<br />\n<br />\n出到線嘅參選人DQ咗的話 會由自己指定plan b出選</blockquote>"},{"pid":"50adba7c4a5130ba6f81ca3d693076e17eb2acf5","tid":2099004,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bebfd00925e152111c326542b23c6c20a4d8e2e","tid":2099004,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:22:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d273f2d6b661fe22ab42f95be242750d3cf61629","tid":2099004,"uid":193371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:22:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c85cb9da54319b763f5271352cf0e10dc26040ba","tid":2099004,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB